            <bio>
               <p>Sylvie Thouësny received a B.A. in German literature and a B.Sc. in computational linguistics. She is currently a Ph.D. student at Dublin City University, Ireland. Her areas of research focus on language learner modeling and feedback and include several aspects of computational linguistics such as error analysis, human-computer interaction, and ICALL system design and development.</p>
